    <h1>ez_content_name</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"contentLayout2">=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout two-right-sidebar" data-layout=3D"two-right-side=
bar">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h4 id=3D"ez_content_name-Description">Description</h4>
<p><code>ez_content_name()</code> is a Twig helper which allows displaying =
a Content item's name in the current language.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
If the current language cannot be found as a translation for content, the n=
ame in the main language is always returned. This behavior is identical whe=
n forcing a language.
</div>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"ez_content_name-PrototypeandArguments">Prototype and Arguments</h=
4>
<p><code><strong>ez_content_name(</strong> eZ\Publish\API\Repository\Values=
\Content\Content <strong>content</strong>[, string&nbsp;<strong>forcedLangu=
age</strong>]&nbsp;<strong>)<br><strong>ez_content_name(</strong></strong><=
strong><strong>contentInfo</strong></strong>[, string&nbsp;<strong><strong>=
forcedLanguage</strong><span>]&nbsp;</span><strong>)</strong>&nbsp;</strong=
></code></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Argument name</th>
<th colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>content</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>eZ\Publish\API\Repository\Va=
lues\Content\Content<br></code><strong>or</strong><code><br><span>eZ\Publis=
h\API\Repository\Values\Content\ContentInfo</span>&nbsp;</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Content or ContentInfo object the displayable fi=
eld belongs to.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>forcedLanguage</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>string</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Locale we want the content name tr=
anslation in (e.g. "fre-FR"). Null by default (takes current locale)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"ez_content_name-Usage">Usage</h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">&lt;h2&gt;Content name in current language: {{ ez_content_name(&nbs=
p;content ) }}&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Content name in current language, from ContentInfo: {{ ez_content=
_name( content.contentInfo ) }}&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Content name in french (forced): {{ ez_content_name( content, "fr=
e-FR" ) }}&lt;/h2&gt;</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"ez_content_name-EquivalentPHPcode">Equivalent PHP code</h4>
<h5 id=3D"ez_content_name-GettingthetranslatednameforaContentitem">Getting =
the translated name for a Content item</h5>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">// Assuming we're in a controller action
$translationHelper =3D $this-&gt;get( 'exponential.translation_helper' );
&nbsp;
// From Content
$translatedContentName =3D $translationHelper-&gt;getTranslatedContentName(=
 $content );
// From ContentInfo
$translatedContentName =3D $translationHelper-&gt;getTranslatedContentNameB=
yContentInfo( $contentInfo );</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h5 id=3D"ez_content_name-Forcingaspecificlanguage">Forcing a specific lang=
uage</h5>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">// Assuming we're in a controller action
$translatedContentName =3D $this-&gt;get( 'exponential.translation_helper' )-=
&gt;getTranslatedName( $content, 'fre-FR' );</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
